caption.p: Cyclic voltammetry curves of the first and the 500th scan of the AACVD vanadate bronze for 15% Ag loading at 450 °C on fluorine-doped SnO 2 precoated glass substrates overlapped on FE-SEM image (FE-SEM image for x50,000 as inset). The scan rate for the cyclic voltammetry curves was 10 mV s −1 [ 66].
